title: Kourtney Kardashian’s Bikini Booty Leads Today’s Star Sightings
text:
Kourtney Kardashian is doing just fine without Scott Disick . As her ex-boyfriend continues to galavant around Miami with a bevy of scantily-clad women , the mom-of-three shared a photo that proves baby’s still got back. 
Taking to Instagram, the mom-of-three recently posted a picture of herself and sister Kim Kardashian showing off their curves in matching white bikinis. 
“I don’t think you ready for this jelly,” Kourtney captioned the shot, quoting Destiny’s Child’s “Bootylicious.” A photo posted by Kourtney Kardashian (@kourtneykardash) on Jan 31, 2017 at 7:23pm PST 
The sexy snap followed an explosive fight between Scott and Kim and Kris Jenner during their family vacation in Costa Rica. According to reports , Scott had secretly invited a woman on the trip without telling the rest of the clan. Kim and Kris confronted the 33-year-old about his female companion, and Scott was seen flying to Miami alone soon after the heated argument. 
Earlier this week, Scott was photographed packing PDA with several ladies at his Florida hotel. Meanwhile, Kourtney was seen taking their kids to an arts class in Calabasas, Calif.
